sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Platform Admin
    participant CLI as kubectl-odh<br/>(odh-cli)
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant DSC as DataScienceCluster<br/>Singleton CR
    participant OLM as OLM<br/>Subscriptions/CSVs
    participant Workloads as Workload CRs<br/>(Notebooks, ISVCs, etc.)
    participant FS as Local Filesystem
    participant GH as GitHub<br/>raw.githubusercontent.com<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Admin,Workloads: Flow 1: Lint / Upgrade Readiness Assessment (37 checks)
        Admin->>CLI: kubectl odh lint [--checks=...] [--json]
        CLI->>K8s: GET DataScienceCluster (singleton)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: DSC spec + status (version detection)
        CLI->>K8s: GET DSCInitialization (singleton)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: DSCI (namespace, ServiceMesh state)
        CLI->>K8s: LIST Subscriptions, CSVs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: OLM operator status (cert-manager, servicemesh)
        CLI->>K8s: LIST PackageManifests<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: Catalog availability (Service Mesh v3)
        CLI->>K8s: LIST Notebooks, InferenceServices,<br/>ServingRuntimes, DSPAs, RayClusters,<br/>PyTorchJobs, GuardrailsOrchestrators,<br/>LlamaStackDistributions, LLMInferenceServices<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: Workload resources (all namespaces)
        CLI->>K8s: LIST ClusterQueues, LocalQueues<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: Kueue resources (data integrity check)
        CLI->>K8s: GET ClusterVersion<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: OpenShift version
        CLI-->>Admin: DiagnosticResult[]\n(conditions, impact levels, impacted objects)\nFormats: table | JSON | YAML
    end

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over Admin,FS: Flow 2: Backup Workloads (Concurrent Pipeline)
        Admin->>CLI: kubectl odh backup [--workload-type=...] [--namespace=...]
        CLI->>K8s: LIST target workloads (Discovery stage)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: Workload resources
        par Dependency Resolution (parallel workers)
            CLI->>K8s: GET ConfigMaps referenced by Notebooks<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
            K8s-->>CLI: ConfigMap data
            CLI->>K8s: GET Secrets referenced by Notebooks<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
            K8s-->>CLI: Secret metadata
            CLI->>K8s: GET PVCs referenced by Notebooks<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
            K8s-->>CLI: PVC specs
            CLI->>K8s: GET DSPA external dependencies<br/>(9 JQ paths: storage, DB, CA, custom)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
            K8s-->>CLI: DSPA dependency resources
        end
        CLI->>FS: Write YAML files (workloads + dependencies)
        CLI-->>Admin: Backup complete (file paths)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over Admin,K8s: Flow 3: Migration - Kueue to RHBOK (Two-Phase)
        Admin->>CLI: kubectl odh migrate prepare kueue-to-rhbok
        CLI->>K8s: GET ClusterQueues, LocalQueues, ConfigMaps<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: Current Kueue resources
        CLI->>FS: Write backup YAML files
        CLI-->>Admin: Prepare complete (step progress tree)

        Admin->>CLI: kubectl odh migrate run kueue-to-rhbok [--dry-run]
        CLI->>K8s: CREATE Subscription (RHBOK operator)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: Subscription created
        CLI->>K8s: PATCH ConfigMaps (add reconciliation-prevention annotation)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: ConfigMaps annotated
        CLI->>K8s: PATCH DataScienceCluster (managementState)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: DSC patched
        CLI->>K8s: GET ClusterQueues, LocalQueues (verify preserved)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: Resources verified
        CLI-->>Admin: Migration complete (step progress tree)
    end

    rect rgb(243, 229, 245)
        Note over Admin,GH: Flow 4: Dependency Check
        Admin->>CLI: kubectl odh deps [--refresh]
        opt --refresh flag
            CLI->>GH: GET odh-gitops/values.yaml<br/>HTTPS/443, No Auth
            GH-->>CLI: Dependency manifest YAML
        end
        CLI->>K8s: LIST Subscriptions, CSVs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: Installed operators
        CLI->>K8s: LIST CRDs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>CLI: Available CRDs
        CLI-->>Admin: Dependency status (installed/missing/version)
    end
